% Button pushed function: AllBandsButton function AllBandsButtonPushed(app, event) app.SubdeltaCheckBox.Value = 1; app.DeltaCheckBox.Value = 1; app.ThetaCheckBox.Value = 1; app.AlphaCheckBox.Value = 1; app.SigmaCheckBox.Value = 1; app.BetaCheckBox.Value = 1; app.GammalowCheckBox.Value = 1; app.FullbandCheckBox.Value = 1; app.SleepbandCheckBox.Value = 1;
