% Value changed function: % InterpolatemanuallyidentifiedbadchannelsCheckBox function InterpolatemanuallyidentifiedbadchannelsCheckBoxValueChanged(app, event) value = app.InterpolatemanuallyidentifiedbadchannelsCheckBox.Value;
